message.body: so except for putting it up on the wall on monday morning, i'm officially done with my final portfolio! crazy!
Woah. How'd you get done so fast? I still have like 8 or 9 to do.
i worked from 2:30 to 10:30 yesterday, haha. and pressed everything today. you're still making good progress, though!
That's a serious amount of work. Wow.
i made up for it by doing literally nothing (but pressing those pictures) today. like seriously. i slept in until 11 and took a 3 hour nap.
Haha ok. You're a lazy bum.
that's what i like to hear! and since it's the weekend now, technically, i feel almost obligated to keep doing nothing. it's great.
I'm gonna have to start working harder. Sort of haven't started studying for my exam on Monday.
nooooo, boooo. that's what sundays are for.
